Madison, however, is not New Glarus and needs to be met at a higher standard.
I am reminded of a comment a friend from Ireland used recently, "It lacks something".
I know that it is focused on specialty hard liquor drinks for the kid set and is probably jammed on Thursday, Friday, and Saturday.
However, we were there on Sunday.
I tried to order the moule frites, but they only had enough for part of our table.
I did, however, get to try them.
Merchant needs to visit Bistro V to see how moule frites are supposed to be done.
